gram\": \"virtually every person\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 803}, {\"ngram\": \"a basketball\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 839}, {\"ngram\": \"a rotation-level guard\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 878}, {\"ngram\": \"theNBA\", \"from\": 882, \"to\": 888}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us say there is an average of three of those players on 30 NBA teams - that is 90 spots.\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 982, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 953, \"end\": 956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.975794330254585e-39, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 896}, {\"ngram\": \"an average\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 920}, {\"ngram\": \"those players\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 946}, {\"ngram\": \"90 spots\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 981}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are 18 teams in the EuroLeague, and let us count two from each of those teams, bringing us to 36.\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 1086, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1009, \"end\": 1019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/EuroLeague\", \"score\": 0.9999999886231309, \"rank\": 1.1376971577728388e-08, \"text\": \"EuroLeague\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/EuroLeague\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/EuroLeague\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"18 teams\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1001}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1031}, {\"ngram\": \"those teams\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1066}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1079}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Perhaps 20 other teams in the world are really on that level.\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1148, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"20 other teams\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1109}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1122}, {\"ngram\": \"that level\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1147}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That is 40 more really excellent jobs, giving us 166 gigs for basketball players 6-foot-5 and under in the world.\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1262, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"40 more really excellent jobs\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1186}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1197}, {\"ngram\": \"166 gigs\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1206}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball players\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1229}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can quibble with the math, but we are in the ballpark.\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1321, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the math\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1292}, {\"ngram\": \"the ballpark\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1320}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Well,Shai Gilgeous-Alexanderis 6-6, so perhaps he does not fit here.\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no questioning that with his (comparatively) slight and lanky 195-pound frame, plus the amount of time he holds the ball for theOklahoma City Thunder, he is a guard.\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1568, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no questioning\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1417}, {\"ngram\": \"his (comparatively) slight and lanky 195-pound frame\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1480}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1505}, {\"ngram\": \"the ball\", \"from\": 1515, \"to\": 1523}, {\"ngram\": \"theOklahoma City Thunder\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1552}, {\"ngram\": \"a guard\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1567}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not only does he have one of those 166 jobs, but he made All-NBA first team last year, made the FIBA World Cup All-Star team in September and is the only player with a remote chance to beat out 7-footerNikola Joki\\u0107for the MVP award this year.\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1811, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1791, \"end\": 1794, \"title\